kah","tag-generosity-al-karm","tag-monotheism-tawhid","tag-allah-names-asma-ul-husna","tag-peace-al-salam","tag-prayer-al-salat","tag-supplication-al-dua","tag-al-tashahhud","tag-al-taslim-tasleem","tag-worship-al-ibadah"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-bU","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":33923,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/01\/13\/istighfar-after-salah\/","url_meta":{"origin":738,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Seeking forgiveness, supplicating after prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 13, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Thawban reported: When the Messenger of Allah peace and blessings be upon him, finished his prayer, he would seek forgiveness from Allah three times and he would say, \u201cO Allah, You are peace and from You is peace. Blessed are You, Majestic and Generous.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 591 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2067,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/11\/tashahhud-sitting-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":738,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Tashahhud: What to say when sitting in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 11, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: While praying behind the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, we were saying, \u201cPeace be upon Allah, peace be upon this person.\u201d The Prophet told us one day, \"Verily, Allah Himself is Peace. When one of you sits in prayer, let him say,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;",