c":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33020,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/01\/prophets-dua-after-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":738,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dua: The Prophet\u2019s supplication after finishing prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 1, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Mughirah ibn Shu\u2019bah reported: When the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, finished the prayer and invoked peace, he would say, \u201cThere is no God but Allah, alone without partner. To him belongs the dominion, all praise, and he has power over all things. O Allah, none\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4437,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/07\/end-salat-salaam-rahmah\/","url_meta":{"origin":738,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Salat: The Prophet ends prayer with peace, mercy","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 7, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Wa\u2019il ibn Hujr reported: I prayed with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he would end by invoking peace on his right side, saying, \u201cPeace be upon you, the mercy of Allah, and His blessings,\u201d and again to his left side, saying, \u201cPeace and mercy of Allah\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/738","targetHints":{"allo